text: Atmosphere is very relaxing and rooms are very spacious. Drinks and snacks are refillable as well!
Nice ambience and clean room. Refillable drink
Friendly staff and nice place for gatherings.

Great customer service, the staff were friendly and approachable, even nice enough to let me come in and play darts, and as a bonus even gave me a 10% discount on the Vodka sprite cocktail and free snacks too even though I'm I didn't sing at the karaoke box. 10/10 would definitely come again and bring a girl or two along haha
Great place to hang out with family and friends.
